data.description: Indulge in Miami Beach living in this oceanfront building with ocean and sunset views from the spacious layout spanning almost 1,200 sqft. One large master suite with the floor plan allowing a second bedroom/den with ocean views. 1 parking space included impact windows as well - Building undergoing improvements, amenities include a pool, sauna, community room, and a gym. Blocks away from iconic hotels like 1 Hotel, Faena and Edition, as well as top-rated restaurant - or enjoy the boardwalk right in your backyard.
